Ted's Vim Setup
===============

Installing
----------

1. Clone this repository into either ~/.vim or some other directory

2. If you cloned this repository into something other than ~/.vim then make a symlink from ~/.vim to your new clone

3. Create a symlink from ~/.vimrc to the vimrc file in this repository

4. To initialize the submodules the first time, run:

    git submodule init

5. To update the submodules, run:

    git submodule update

That's it!

Useful gitconfig stanza
-----------------------

[alias]
  lo = log --graph --decorate --pretty=oneline --abbrev-commit
  lol = log --graph --decorate --pretty=oneline --abbrev-commit --branches --not --remotes
  lola = log --graph --decorate --pretty=oneline --abbrev-commit --branches
  lolaa = log --graph --decorate --pretty=oneline --abbrev-commit --all
